OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774293066
OL,3,CBritish man jailed in Iran criticises
OL,4,CGovernment for abandonment in war zone
OL,6,FA man from East Sussex who has been
OL,7,Fjailed alongside his wife for 10 years
OL,8,Fin Iran for spying has criticised the
OL,9,FGovernment for abandoning them in a
OL,10,Fwar zone.
OL,12,FSpeaking from prison, Craig Foreman
OL,13,Fsaid he and his partner, Lindsay, feel
OL,14,F"let down, alone and completely
OL,15,Ffrustrated" with how their situation
OL,16,Fis being handled.
OL,18,FThe 53-year-olds were jailed following
OL,19,Ftheir arrest in January 2025 while
OL,20,Ftravelling through Iran during an
OL,21,Faround-the-world trip by motorcycle.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
